		["Item-203932"] = {
			["base"] = {
				["title"] = "Sentient Book",
				["text"] = {
					"OW! Who did that? Who just opened me up? Oh, it's like someone grabbed the sides of my ribcage and tore it open! Oooh, my spine! Wait, someone's looking at me. Someone has torn me open and is looking inside me. Can they hear what I'm thinking? And how did I get here?\r\n\r\nHey! Hey you! What are you looking at? Gods, why are you scrying my innards? Oh, the pain! Please, I beg of you, close me. Close me! I don't know how this happened, but I can feel... my life force... fading away. Oh, gods... my skin... my... cover? I'm a book? And I'm dying... and now I am... dead. THE END.",
